<section>
  <h2>Tron</h2>
  <a class="preview" href="/more_hello_world/tron/"><img src="/images/hello_world/tron.png" /></a>
  <p>Let's give our page a retro, high-tech feel inspired by Tron.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>Setup</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Create a new stylesheet named <code>tron_style.css</code>.</li>
    <li>
      <p>Link your new stylesheet to your HTML file.</p>
      <p>Change your <code>link</code> element to look like this:</p>
      <pre><code>&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;tron_style.css&quot;&gt;</code></pre>
    </li>
  </ol>
</section>

<%= partial 'shared/colors', locals: {colors: data.colors.hello_world_tron} %>

